{"tid":2216471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑警出聲政府配合］ 以後只有新聞處已登記記者才可出席政府記招及活動","createTime":"2020-09-24T16:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T16:45:13.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3e40f1d88a75c1e2462f86d68ad0e1d3ceff146d","tid":2216471,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"警方修改傳媒定義，只承認已登記政府新聞處新聞發布系統（GNMIS）的傳媒。政府新聞處疑為配合警方說法，今發稿聲稱只有在系統登記的傳媒，才會獲邀及容許出席政府記招及傳媒活動。<br />\n<br />\n新聞處全稿以「登記用戶」借代GNMIS系統中的已登記傳媒，稱GNMIS系統用於向傳媒提供政府新聞稿等資料，並向「登記用戶」發放政府採訪通知。處方聲稱，一般而言只有「登記用戶」才會獲邀和容許出席政府記者招待會及傳媒活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/EVDO5IOXQZFBLN6NQ45TQZWLCU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2xSsIKaAZyEivyS8IkrUifyo7GjDFmAmLyRZvH2cNHlmSzcXublibVgh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FEVDO5IOXQZFBLN6NQ45TQZWLCU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2xSsIKaAZyEivyS8IkrUifyo7GjDFmAmLyRZvH2cNHlmSzcXublibVgh8&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=6581a152\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FEVDO5IOXQZFBLN6NQ45TQZWLCU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2xSsIKaAZyEivyS8IkrUifyo7GjDFmAmLyRZvH2cNHlmSzcXublibVgh8&h=53323f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/EVDO5IOXQZFBLN6NQ45TQZWLCU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2xSsIKaAZyEivyS8IkrUifyo7GjDFmAmLyRZvH2cNHlmSzcXublibVgh8</a>"},{"pid":"8c5afe37519e574e4800cec89cd5e5bbbc08ce63","tid":2216471,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"警權無限大+1"}]}